data.description:
Right in the heart of Hodges Blvd in the Pablo Bay community, this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2,552 sqft home is ready for its new owner. The stucco home features a formal dining room and living room combo, and breakfast bar in the kitchen. Special qualities throughout include ceramic tile throughout the main living areas, home/theater speaker system, front door and sliding back door replaced 2 years ago (Type 1 Series Andersen Doors) finished garage floor, integrated vacuum in garage, a Pelican water softener, and don't miss the sidewalk pavers that lead you to your backyard Lakeview! 

All Carpets brand new, Roof 2 years old, A/C 3 years old, and Hot Water  4 years old. If buyer chooses First Coast Mortgage NMLS #1953441, a $2,000 credit will be applied towards closing costs.  Christopher Austin NMLS  NMLS #648815. This is not a commitment to lend.  Equal Housing Opportunity.
